quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  4,116,"God does not forgive one´s associating [others] with Him; He forgives anyone He wishes to for anything beyond that. Anyone who associates [others] with God has strayed far afield"
  4,117,They only appeal to females instead of to Him; they only call upon some upstart Satan
  4,118,"God cursed him, and he said: \"I shall take some of Your servants as a stipulated portion"
  4,119,I will lead them astray and urge them on. I will order them to slit the ears on livestock and order them to alter what God has created. Anyone who adopts Satan as a patron instead of God has obviously lost out
  4,120,"He promises them [things] and urges them on; yet Satan promises them nothing except delusion"
  4,121,Those will have Hell as their refuge and find no escape from it
  4,122,"We will show the ones who believe and perform honorable gardens through which rivers flow, to live there forever. God´s true; who is more reliable in the way he speaks than God"
  4,123,"There is nothing in your saying ´Amens\" nor in the way the People of the Book say \"Amen\". Anyone who commits evil will be rewarded accordingly and not find any patron nor protector for himself besides God"
  4,124,"Anyone who performs honorable deeds, whether it is a man or a woman, provided he is a believer, those will enter the Garden and not be speck"
  4,125,Who is finer in religion than someone who peacefully commends his person to God while he acts kindly and follows the sect of Abraham the Enquirer? God adopted Abraham as a bosom friend
  4,126,God holds whatever is in Heaven and whatever is on Earth; God embraces everything